note:
1. Hi Albina, If they are good then yes. Can you send me some CVs? Best, VInce
2. Thanks, going to take a look in the weekend and get back to you.
3. Do you have any testers? exploratory testing and perhaps someone that can do test automation as well
4. igor@pzaz.tv is my collegua. Monday 1PM CET we have a 20 min slot. Does that work for you? Google Meet.

Company Name: Pzaz TV

Company Website: http://www.pzaz.tv

Contact Person: Igor Lakic

Product: Pzaz provides the perfect mix of free and paid tv channels, video on demand, a free TV guide, and all your paid subscriptions combined in one place, making it super easy to indulge in great television.

Country-Location: UK

Target Audience: around Europe

Immediate Requirement: Igor is looking for QA testers to fix bugs - 2 people. 
1. Senior/middle tester with 1 - up to 2 years of experience. 
2. Junior tester with basic knowledge - for example go to the site and press 100 buttons; report the bugs - button not working; if you sign in and you will send on another URL - fix it.
They will teach if something is not clear. Full Time. 


Next Step: Send the information about our company and CV’s of the most suitable candidates.

Next Contact Date: scheduled an interview on Friday 2nd of June at 2 PM CET time.

We Interviewed candidates for Pzaz TV company

Candidates:

Maxim https://rh-s.com/web-developer/qa/maxim-h/
Working as a QA tester for 1 year - analyst job, application of technologies. 

Johnathan will provide a small test for Maxim. When they will receive the result we will decide how to move on.

We Interviewed candidates for Pzaz TV company


Aleksei https://rh-s.com/developer/aleksei-g/
QA tester. Can work with Figma. 

Jonathan said that Aleksei is a very good choice for them.
But first he would like to review a test task. And then they will decide.

client_candidates.comment: Sergey: He introduced himself perfectly, the client liked it. They discussed some cases regarding the web-site which should be done (the client will send us additional information). As the client believes that Sergei is a right fit for doing such tasks, she is going to hire him part-time.

Alla: She introduced herself perfectly, the client liked it, especially that Alla now is in Germany. She checked the web-site and shared her thoughts about what she would do and modernize as well as she estimated how much time it would take. On the other hand, the client doesn’t want to remake her entire web-site. For now she is thinking about using a 40 hour package for Alla.

Bohdan: He introduced himself perfectly, the client liked it, especially all of the videos he had done. She thinks that Bohdan is the best video editor from our web-site. Also he said that he is working on his pronunciation and studying philology. The client also wants him to hire 40 hours.

работал по 4ч в день
